gitCommit.subject: fix: update E2E tests to use valid URLs and UUIDs, improve error handling
gitCommit.body:
fix: update E2E tests to use valid URLs and UUIDs, improve error handling

- Updated E2E test cases to use full URLs (http://localhost:5000) for API calls and page navigation.
- Changed hardcoded IDs in MemStorage to valid UUIDs for better test reliability.
- Adjusted Playwright configuration to use Playwright-managed Chromium instead of system Chromium.
- Enhanced error handling in tests to provide clearer context for failures.
- Increased timeout values in tests to prevent premature failures due to slow responses.

fix: update E2E tests to use valid URLs and UUIDs, improve error handling

- Updated E2E test cases to use full URLs (http://localhost:5000) for API calls and page navigation.
- Changed hardcoded IDs in MemStorage to valid UUIDs for better test reliability.
- Adjusted Playwright configuration to use Playwright-managed Chromium instead of system Chromium.
- Enhanced error handling in tests to provide clearer context for failures.
- Increased timeout values in tests to prevent premature failures due to slow responses.
